short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Saves your quality and custom speed changes on Uplearn.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Allows you to set custom speeds on uplearn (2.25x - 3.00x) and forces the quality on every video to be whatever is chosen in the extension (as uplearn defaults to 540p every time).

Github page: https://github.com/hifrens/Uplearn-Extension
